patch.description:
Pin or unpin a tag via ``PATCH /api/tags/{id}/pinned``.

``{pinned: true}`` pins the tag in the sidebar filter panel;
``{pinned: false}`` unpins it. 404 if absent.

Show or hide a message from the context window (G3).

``{hidden: true}`` drops the message from the next prompt context;
``{hidden: false}`` restores it. Returns the updated row. 404 when absent.

TagPinnedUpdate.description:
Request body for ``PATCH /api/tags/{id}/pinned``.

``pinned=true`` pins the tag in the sidebar filter panel;
``pinned=false`` unpins it. Mirrors :class:`SessionPinnedUpdate`.
